209 export function activate_animation_second_part(material) {
210   if (general_config.grid != null) {
211     general_config.grid.children[0].material = material;
212   }
213   if (general_config.grid_plane != null) {
214     general_config.grid_plane.children[0].material = material;
215   }
216   recreate_scene();
217 }

1098 export function create_random_points_cloud(
1099   MesoNH_O_array,
1100   MesoNH_U_array,
1101   MesoNH_V_array,
1102   grid,
1103   id_sbl_array,
1104   id_meso_array,
1105   temperature_scale,
1106   THAT,
1107   THAT_W,
1108   HCanopy,
1109   HCanopy_w
1110 ) {
1111   /*
1112 		creation des nuages de points 3D
1113 	*/
1114 
1115   let tab_temp = [];
1116   //let tab_temp2 = general_config.temp_values;
1117 
1118   general_config.temp_values = [];
1119   var ni = general_config.data_ni,
1120     nj = general_config.data_nj;
1121 
1122   var coord_array = [];
1123   var colors = [];
1124   var sizes = [];
1125   var transparency_factor_array = [];
1126   var custompercentagearray = [];
1127   var z_position_array = [];
1128   var x_position_array = [];
1129   var y_position_array = [];
1130 
1131   var h_position_array = [];
1132 
1133   var voxel_level_array = [];
1134 
1135   general_config.z_min = null;
1136   general_config.z_max = null;
1137   general_config.x_min = null;
1138   general_config.x_max = null;
1139   general_config.y_min = null;
1140   general_config.y_max = null;
1141 
1142   general_config.h_min = null;
1143   general_config.h_max = null;
1144 
1145   for (var m = 0; m < id_sbl_array.length; m++) {
1146     for (var j = 0; j < nj; j++) {
1147       for (var i = 0; i < ni; i++) {
1148         var index_1 = j * ni + i;
1149 
1150         var id = id_sbl_array[m];
1151         var temp = parseFloat(MesoNH_O_array[index_1]["teb_" + id]);
1152 
1153         var index_sup_1 = j * ni + i + (id - 1) * ni * nj;
1154         var index_sup_2 = j * ni + i + id * ni * nj;
1155         var h =
1156           general_config.data_volume_3D["limit_teb"][index_sup_1] -
1157           MesoNH_O_array[index_1].zs +
1158           (general_config.data_volume_3D["limit_teb"][index_sup_2] -
1159             general_config.data_volume_3D["limit_teb"][index_sup_1]) /
1160             2;
1161         var h_w =
1162           general_config.data_volume_3D["limit_teb"][index_sup_1] -
1163           MesoNH_O_array[index_1].zs;
1164 
1165         // pour 'effectifs egaux', tableau temporaire
1166         tab_temp.push(temp);
1167 
1168         var x_o = MesoNH_O_array[index_1].x - general_config.Coord_X_paris;
1169         var y_o = MesoNH_O_array[index_1].y - general_config.Coord_Y_paris;
1170         var z_o = MesoNH_O_array[index_1].zs + h;
1171 
1172         var l_x = (MesoNH_O_array[index_1].x - MesoNH_U_array[index_1].x) * 2;
1173         var l_y = (MesoNH_O_array[index_1].y - MesoNH_V_array[index_1].y) * 2;
1174         var l_z = (h - h_w) * 2;
1175 
1176         if (general_config.h_min != null && general_config.h_max != null) {
1177           if (h_w < general_config.h_min) {
1178             general_config.h_min = h_w;
1179           }
1180           if (h_w + l_z > general_config.h_max) {
1181             general_config.h_max = h_w + l_z;
1182           }
1183         } else {
1184           general_config.h_min = h_w;
1185           general_config.h_max = h_w + l_z;
1186         }
1187 
1188         if (general_config.z_min != null && general_config.z_max != null) {
1189           if (z_o - l_z / 2 < general_config.z_min) {
1190             general_config.z_min = z_o - l_z / 2;
1191           }
1192           if (z_o + l_z / 2 > general_config.z_max) {
1193             general_config.z_max = z_o + l_z / 2;
1194           }
1195         } else {
1196           general_config.z_min = z_o - l_z / 2;
1197           general_config.z_max = z_o + l_z / 2;
1198         }
1199 
1200         if (general_config.x_min != null && general_config.x_max != null) {
1201           if (x_o - l_x / 2 < general_config.x_min) {
1202             general_config.x_min = x_o - l_x / 2;
1203           }
1204           if (x_o + l_x / 2 > general_config.x_max) {
1205             general_config.x_max = x_o + l_x / 2;
1206           }
1207         } else {

3639 export function hexToRgb(hex) {
3640   var result = /^#?([a-f\d]{2})([a-f\d]{2})([a-f\d]{2})$/i.exec(hex);
3641 
3642   return result
3643     ? {
3644         r: parseInt(result[1], 16),
3645         g: parseInt(result[2], 16),
3646         b: parseInt(result[3], 16),
3647       }
3648     : null;

3651 export function approximateColor1ToColor2ByPercent(color1, color2, percent) {
3652   var red1 = parseInt(color1[1] + color1[2], 16);
3653   var green1 = parseInt(color1[3] + color1[4], 16);
3654   var blue1 = parseInt(color1[5] + color1[6], 16);
3655 
3656   var red2 = parseInt(color2[1] + color2[2], 16);
3657   var green2 = parseInt(color2[3] + color2[4], 16);
3658   var blue2 = parseInt(color2[5] + color2[6], 16);
3659 
3660   var red = Math.round(mix(red1, red2, percent));
3661   var green = Math.round(mix(green1, green2, percent));
3662   var blue = Math.round(mix(blue1, blue2, percent));
3663 
3664   return generateHex(red, green, blue);
3665 }

3667 export function generateHex(r, g, b) {
3668   r = r.toString(16);
3669   g = g.toString(16);
3670   b = b.toString(16);
3671 
3672   while (r.length < 2) {
3673     r = "0" + r;
3674   }
3675   while (g.length < 2) {
3676     g = "0" + g;
3677   }
3678   while (b.length < 2) {
3679     b = "0" + b;
3680   }
3681 
3682   return "#" + r + g + b;
3683 }

3685 export function mix(start, end, percent) {
3686   return start + percent * (end - start);

4984 export function getHCLcolor(tableau, temp, percentage, HCLscale) {
4985   let color, i;
4986   let tab_temp = tableau.slice();
4987   let array = [];
4988   let nb_arr = general_config.nb_array;
4989 
4990   if (general_config.active_color_class == "ecarts_egaux") {
4991     let temp_min = general_config.temp_array[0];
4992     let temp_max = general_config.temp_array[1];
4993     let ecart = (temp_max - temp_min) / nb_arr;
4994     for (i = 0; i < nb_arr; ++i) {
4995       //creation de n sous tableaux vides
4996       array.push([]);
4997     }
4998     tab_temp.forEach((temperature) => {
4999       for (i = 0; i < array.length; ++i) {
5000         if (
5001           temperature >= temp_min + ecart * i &&
5002           temperature <= temp_min + ecart * (i + 1)
5003         ) {
5004           array[i].push(temperature);
5005         }
5006       }
5007     });
5008     /*
5009          on peut 'return array' ici pour avoir le tableau composé des sous tableaux
5010         */
5011   } else if (general_config.active_color_class == "effectifs_egaux") {
5012     let nbeMaxDeVals = Math.ceil(tab_temp.length / nb_arr);
5013     for (i = 0; i < nb_arr; ++i) {
5014       if (tab_temp.length / (nb_arr - i) < nbeMaxDeVals && nbeMaxDeVals > 1) {
5015         array.push(tab_temp.splice(0, nbeMaxDeVals - 1));
5016       } else {
5017         array.push(tab_temp.splice(0, nbeMaxDeVals));
5018       }
5019     }
5020     /*
5021         on peut 'return array' ici pour avoir le tableau composé des sous tableaux
5022 
5023         */
5024   }
5025   //A adapter quand on changera les couleurs par un .png
5026   for (i = 0; i < nb_arr; ++i) {
5027     if (temp >= array[i][0] && temp <= array[i][array[i].length - 1]) {
5028       color = HCLscale[i];
5029       return color;
5030     }
5031   }
5032   //Ci dessous sert à renvoyer une couleur (pour ne pas que ca bugge) même si les points/plans ne seront pas représentés
5033   if (percentage === 1) {
5034     return HCLscale[nb_arr - 1];
5035   }
5036   if (percentage === 0) {
5037     return HCLscale[0];
5038   }
5039 }

5959 /**
5960  * Cette fonction permet de calculer les temperatures moyennes en degré celsius de chaque niveau teb et de tous
5961  * les niveaux teb dans chaque fichier.
5962  * @return {list} avg_list
5963  */
5964 export function calculate_avg_temperature() {
5965   let avg_list = [];
5966   general_config.netcdf_list.forEach((file) => {
5967     let formatted_date = file.globalData.date.getDate() + "-" + (file.globalData.date.getMonth() + 1) + "-" +  file.globalData.date.getFullYear()+ " " + file.globalData.date.getHours() + ":" + file.globalData.date.getMinutes() + ":" + file.globalData.date.getSeconds() 
5968     let v = {
5969       date1:  new Date(file.globalData.date).getTime(),
5970       date : file.globalData.date,
5971       dateString: formatted_date,
5972       teb_1: 0,
5973       teb_2: 0,
5974       teb_3: 0,
5975       teb_4: 0,
5976       teb_5: 0,
5977       teb_6: 0,
5978       globalAvg: 0
5979     };
5980     let compteur = [0,0,0,0,0,0];
5981     file.listePoints.forEach((point) => {
5982       if (point.teb_1 != 999) {
5983         v.teb_1 += point.teb_1;
5984         compteur[0] += 1;
